$interpreted: Ace: The Aldric family is one of the twelve noble families.
Ace: If even we cannot prevent a thief from sneaking in, how are the people supposed to believe we can protect the nation!!
Ace: This necklace was a gift from the Carlos family. It is a token of loyalty, given specifically to the Aldric family.
Ace: Nothing can happen to this! NOTHING!
Guard (Team 1): Well, well, well. Ain't that sweet. The Aldric family is worried about something other than their daughter Sione.
Guard (Team 2): You big, dumb idiot. You think they're worried about this necklace? They're worried about what Sione gave——
Ace: Who's speaking!?!?
Ace: I don't care who this "Thief of the Gleaming Star" is, there's no way I'm letting him run amok in my house!!
Ace: In fact, I don't even want to see so much as a mouse in my house!!
Ace: GOT IT!?
Guard (Team 2): Yes, sir!!
Joan: Nice rhyme, buddy. But I ain't no mouse. I'm...The Thief of the Gleaming Star!
Guard (Team 1): It's the Thief of the Gleaming Star!
Ace: GET HER!!!!
Joan: Wah! Who knew I had so many suitors!
Joan: As an offering to the stars which chose me on that fateful night, I present you all...with a gift!
Guard (Team 2): Oh no! It's sleeping gas! Everybody, hold your breath!
Ace: No one is permitted...to...steal...the...
Joan: What a breeze~~~
Joan: The necklace of lore and legend...is mine!
Joan: Why he's grabbing the box so tightly? Isn't he asleep?
Ace: Si...one...be with me...always ...
Joan: Eh? Why'd it get so cold all of a sudden?
Joan: This guy's got on quite the smile...wonder what he's dreaming about.
Joan: There's something written on the bottom of this box~
Joan: Let's see...
Joan: That rat!!! Oh, you think you can play me, do you!? Unacceptable!!
Tica: Where am I? I'm not...lost!?
Tica: Crap. I'm in biggg trouble~ I'm supposed to find the Owl Egg.
Tica: I just wanted to kill some time. Never thought it'd actually be hard to find this thing.
Tica: If I don't find it, I'm definitely getting kicked out of school!!
Joan: Who's Sione!!!
Tica: Ooooo, is that people arguing? Let me check it out~
Joan: Speak!!! Who. is. SIONE!?
Edward: Eh? I've never heard of such a name.
Joan: Liar! Then explain how "From Sione" got on the box of your family heirloom!
Edward: I-I-I-I...I have n-n-no idea...!
Joan: Well I do. The necklace some little wench gave you was snatched up and you used those sweet words to trick me into stealing it back! Isn't that right!?
Joan: Very creative, you bittlebucket! Straight out of a romance novel!
Edward: No...no! It's not like that. Let me explain...!
Joan: NO NO NO NO NO!!!!!!
Tica: What's going on here? Arguing's no good~ Let me be the ambassador of justice!
Edward: Oh, wonderful. Sione, you've returned!
Tica: Ehhhhhh!? Why are you calling me Sione?
Joan: So you're the little wench, huh!?
Tica: Eh!? No, you got it all wrong, I'm a senior at the Rune academy.
Joan: What!? Disgusting! Well, I don't care how old you are, interfering in relationships is just plain wrong!
Tica: Wait wait wait wait wait! Look! Look! I can prove I'm not Sione!
Joan: What's this?
Joan: Rune Academy Student ID: Tica Chevalier
Tica: Told you I wasn't Sione~~
Joan: I'm soooo sorry! I was wrong, please forgive me!
Tica: Don't worry about it. I do stuff like that all the time.
Tica: But...I think your friend just ran off with that box.
Joan: Edward? Hey, where'd the box go!?
Tica: I saw him run off in that direction.
Joan: Thank you so much. I must be going!
Tica: Bye-bye~~Hope you two figure things out~
Tica: Wah~that girl can run~
Tica: Hmmm...now that I think of it...I think I've heard that name before...Sione...
Tica: Whatever, can't remember~ Better find that egg!
